{"tid":1478051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老解真係嚟香港,要點應對","createTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:46:19.000Z","uid":294406,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1953ac282fc5d20f8468a0d161d13502675d9aa1","tid":1478051,"uid":294406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"#重要<br />\n<br />\n王丹在臉書撰文指出，如果中共真的派武警進駐香港，「建議港人迅速從街頭撤退，回到家中，儘量少上街，讓全香港變成一座空城。」他說這樣做的好處有四個，第一是全城罷工罷課，且理由充分。第二是全城空無一人，軍人在街上便無所事事，每天還要被國際譴責並承受經濟制裁。第三，軍隊無暴可平，最終只能撤守，港人再度出來抗爭。最後，如此重複，中共必定傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2886201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2886201&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0f5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=f22952ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2886201&h=f8047f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2886201</a>"},{"pid":"4fee819ff71e138253dcffec18b5bb8304fb59b9","tid":1478051,"uid":152630,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"返屋企瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5e58b6666c90ec7a614380afa95988a6716922","tid":1478051,"uid":152508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1953ac282fc5d20f8468a0d161d13502675d9aa1","tid":1478051,"uid":294406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"#重要<br />\n<br />\n王丹在臉書撰文指出，如果中共真的派武警進駐香港，「建議港人迅速從街頭撤退，回到家中，儘量少上街，讓全香港變成一座空城。」他說這樣做的好處有四個，第一是全城罷工罷課，且理由充分。第二是全城空無一人，軍人在街上便無所事事，每天還要被國際譴責並承受經濟制裁。第三，軍隊無暴可平，最終只能撤守，港人再度出來抗爭。最後，如此重複，中共必定傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2886201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2886201&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0f5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=f22952ca\" data-e